<p>Smashwords is a platform for indie authors to publish their work. You can access thousands of free novels in various genres, from romance to science fiction. It’s an excellent way to discover new voices in literature, as many authors often give away their novels as promotional tools. You can download books in multiple formats, making them easy to read on different devices.</p>
<h3>BookRix</h3>
<p>BookRix is an exciting platform for both readers and writers. It offers free access to numerous novels and stories in various genres. Readers can also connect with authors and give feedback on their works. The website is intuitive, making it easy to search for novels based on preferred categories or tags.</p>
